quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,Kasam hai raat ki jabke woh chaa jaaye
  92,2,Aur din ki jabke woh roshan ho
  92,3,Aur us zaat ki jisne nar(male) aur maada(female) ko paida kiya
  92,4,Dar haqeeqat tum logon ki koshishein mukhtalif qism ki hai
  92,5,To jisne (rah e khuda mein) maal diya aur (khuda ki nafarmani se) parhez kiya
  92,6,Aur bhalayi ko sach mana
  92,7,Usko hum aasan raastey kay liye sahulat denge
  92,8,Aur jisne bukhl(kanjoosi) kiya aur (apney khuda se) be niyazi(self-sufficient/independent) barti
  92,9,aur bhalayi ko jhutlaya
  92,10,Usko hum sakht rastey kay liye sahulat dengey
  92,11,Aur uska maal aakhir uske kis kaam aayega jabke woh halaq ho jaye
  92,12,Beshak rasta batana hamare zimmey hai
  92,13,aur dar haqeeqat aakhirat aur duniya dono kay hum hi malik hai
  92,14,Pas maine tumko khabardar kar diya hai bhadakti hui aag se
  92,15,Usmein nahin jhulsega magar woh intihayi badbakth
  92,16,jisne jhutlaya aur mooh phera
  92,17,Aur usse door rakkha jayega woh nihayat parhezgaar
  92,18,Jo paakiza honay ki khatir apna maal deta hai
  92,19,Uspar kisi ka koi ehsan nahin hai jiska badla usey dena ho
  92,20,Woh to sirf apne Rubb-e-bartrar ki raza joii ke liye yeh kaam karta hai
  92,21,Aur zaroor woh (us se) khush hoga